Source.Name: godot-cpp
Source.Summary: C++ bindings for the Godot script API
Source.Description: The C++ bindings for GDNative are built on top of the NativeScript GDNative API and provide a nicer way to "extend" nodes in Godot using C++. This is equivalent to writing scripts in GDScript, but in C++ instead.
